      "text": "人来带过少爷的马，阵前去会佘赛花。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00022",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "佘赛花、四文堂、四女兵、女马童同上，打过合。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00023",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "阵前来了杨家将，不由奴家怒胸膛。提枪拍马往前闯，少时教你无下场。（佘赛花、四文堂、四女兵、女马童、杨继业、四文堂、四上手同钻烟筒下，杨继业、佘赛花同上，同起打，杨继业败下，佘赛花耍枪花下。四上手、四女兵同上，同起打，双下。杨继业败上，佘赛花追上，同起打，杨继业败下，佘赛花追下。杨继业上。）",
      "text_length": 145
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00024",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "且住！看这个丫头杀法厉害，杀得我上天无路，入地无门，这便如何是好！",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00025",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00026",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "七星庙，七星庙！来此已是七星庙，待我下马进庙。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00027",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业下马，进庙。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00028",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "待我将门闭上，在此处躲避一时，再作道理。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00029",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "佘赛花上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00030",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "啊！适才与杨家小将交战，被奴将他杀得大败，他在前面跑，奴在后面赶，来在此地，为何不见？",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00031",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "佘赛花看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00032",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "七星庙，七星庙！想是他在庙中藏躲，看他将庙门关闭，这便怎么处？待奴喊叫一声。呔！杨家小将听着：你家姑娘在此等候，你快开庙门，与姑娘再战三合！",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00033",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "这个丫头，她竟自赶来了！她叫我开门与她再战。你家少爷在庙内安身，任凭你这丫头说得天花乱坠，你少爷就是不开门的了！",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00034",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "看他执意不肯开门，这便如何是好？哦哦有啦，待我吓他一吓。杨家小将，你隐藏庙内，不肯开门，待奴吩咐三军，将庙墙团团围住，四面放起火来，将庙宇烧坏，管叫你死无葬身之地！",
      "text_length": 82
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00035",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，这个丫头言道：吩咐三军，将庙宇烧坏，要叫我死无葬身之地，这便怎好？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00036",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业跪拜。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00037",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "望求神圣保佑，望求神圣保佑！呔，佘赛花丫头，既叫你少爷开门，你少爷敢开庙门，只怕你不敢下马！",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00038",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "你既敢开庙门，你姑娘就敢下马。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00039",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业跪拜。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00040",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "望求神圣多多保佑！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00041",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "你姑娘下马来了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00042",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "待我与你开门！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00043",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "你开来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00044",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "来了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00045",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业开门，佘赛花执枪刺杨继业，杨继业夺枪，绑佘赛花跪地。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00046",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "我看你这丫头，还往哪里走！待我将她的战马，牵进庙来，将庙门关闭了。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00047",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨继业拴马。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00048",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "好杀呀好杀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00049",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "好战哪好战！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00050",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "好跑哇好跑！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00051",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "好赶哪好赶！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00052",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "赶的你家少爷是燕儿不下蛋。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00053",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "赶的你姑娘是一身的透汗。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00054",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "你这丫头，实实的好狠心哪！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00055",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "你的心肠也就不软！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00056",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "怎见得你少爷心狠？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00057",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "你为何将奴家兄长杀死？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00058",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "你就不该赖了我的亲事！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00059",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "那是我爹爹做主，与奴什么相干？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00060",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "你倒推得干净！今日你既被擒，我且问你：你是愿意一死，还是愿意一活？",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00061",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "死是怎样讲，活是怎么说？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00062",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "你要是愿意死呀，我就是这一枪，将你刺死！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00063",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "佘赛花"
      ],
      "text": "这一活呢？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00064",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨继业"
      ],
      "text": "这一活么？来来来，你就与我成亲事、拜天地！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03089001_e00065",
      "play_id": "03089001",
      "scene_id": "03089001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
